Code Description : 

The code contain node js, angularjs , mysql for back-end.

There are some html files which is for front end display the content and response.
First folder which contain the angular js code, in this folder you can get controller of angular js. In this folder I just past 2 controller , in user controller file you can check the code of controller.

For all controller I am using the services.

I also used some directives of angularjs , you can check it under directives folder.

Under the config folder there is some code example of node js.

for node js we are using express framework of node js and as required I also used other module too of node.
